Scraping from www.medscape.com¶

In [1]:
url = "https://www.medscape.com/index/list_13470_0"
In [2]:
import requests

r = requests.get(url)
#r.content

Load the fetched content into a BeautifulSoup object¶

In [3]:
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup

soup = BeautifulSoup(r.content, "html.parser")

In [12]:
urls = ["https://www.medscape.com/index/list_13470_0"]

for i in range(1, 440):     # The range from -0 to -439
    url = f"https://www.medscape.com/index/list_13470_{i}"
    urls.append(url)
